&lt;p&gt;Do you have a passion for working within a paediatric setting and would like to work in a challenging environment? We are looking to recruit to the post of Band 6 Charge Nurse/Sister to work on the Paediatric Ward. There are 2 posts available at 24 hours and 36 hours per week. The post will require you to work a mix of shifts. The busy Children’s Ward has an identified Paediatric Assessment Unit, High Dependency Area, Young Person’s Area and a Dedicated Day Case Ward. We can offer a range of training opportunities. We require someone who is adaptable to work in all areas of the ward and who is a real team player.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further information, please contact Louise Garratt, Lead Nurse Paediatrics on 01384 456111 extension 3423 or email louise.garratt1@nhs.net&lt;/p&gt;
